<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="slow-adj">slow <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /sləʊ/    美 /sloʊ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>慢的；缓慢的：</strong></h4>
<p>反 quick / fast </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a slow stream
缓慢的溪流</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My watch is <strong>five minutes slow</strong>.
我的表慢了5分钟。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I missed the fast train and had to get the slow one.
我没赶上快车，只得坐慢车了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>迟迟不...的；慢吞吞的：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>(be) slow in doing / to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The police were slow in coming.
警察迟迟不来。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>迟钝的；笨的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a slow learner
迟钝的学习者</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>slowly /'sləʊli/ adv   </p></div>